### ── 1. Create course ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Copy the returned `id` into http-client.env.json as `courseId`
POST {{baseUrl}}/play4change/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sustainability Basics",
  "subjectDomain": "sustainability",
  "moduleTitle": "Introduction to Sustainability",
  "moduleObjective": "Understand the core principles of sustainable living",
  "durationDays": 3
}

### ── 2. Enroll user in course ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Copy the returned `subscriptionId` — enrolledAt is your dayIndex anchor
### Copy the returned `moduleId` into http-client.env.json as `moduleId`
POST {{baseUrl}}/play4change/courses/{{courseId}}/enroll
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### ── 3. Get today's task (uses enrolledAt to compute dayIndex server-side) ────
### First call: assigns a random task from pool
### Repeat call: returns the same task (idempotency)
### Copy the returned `userTaskId` into http-client.env.json as `userTaskId`
GET {{baseUrl}}/play4change/tasks/today
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### ── 4. Get today's task — different user (should get different task) ──────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/play4change/tasks/today
X-User-Id: user2

### ── 5. Submit MCQ answer ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### selectedOption 0 = first option shown (after shuffle)
POST {{baseUrl}}/play4change/tasks/{{userTaskId}}/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "selectedOption": 3
}

### ── 6. Submit TODO_ACTION answer ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/play4change/tasks/{{userTaskId}}/submit
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

{
  "textAnswer": "I brought my reusable bag to the supermarket today instead of using plastic bags."
}

### ── 7. Get daily task (old endpoint, still works) ────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/play4change/tasks/daily?moduleId={{moduleId}}&dayIndex=0
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### ── Health check ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### ── Prometheus metrics ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/prometheus
